## Confidence statement

Findings are drawn from the raw message source and open-source infrastructure lookups. Where a claim rests on attacker-supplied data it is identified as such and excluded from conclusions. The URL has not been retrieved, assessment of the landing page is outstanding, and no claim is made about its content.
